{"tid":392101,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"見到「超正伴遊妹」凍未條..加8千嘿咻　男反被告性侵","createTime":"2017-09-08T09:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T10:59:20.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46a2ca846acf55ad54a120e60df53f400bbacbaf","tid":392101,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"基隆一名31歲的宋姓男子透過經紀公司找到22歲小模莉莉（化名）伴遊，見面時被對方的外型吸引，決定臨時加碼8000元發生關係。事後，莉莉遭到公司質疑超時，因為怕被抽成，向公司謊稱被性侵，還向宋男提告。<br />\n<br />\n據《自由時報》報導，宋男今年6月間通過經記公司選到D奶的莉莉，原本協議3小時2萬5千元的伴遊價格，沒想到看到本人之後，見對方外貌姣好就起了色心，決定再加8000元發生關係，最後在女方也同意之下完事。<br />\n<br />\n隔天，莉莉被公司懷疑超時，在交仲介費時被詢問「為什麼這麼晚回公司？」對此，為了不想被多抽成，竟然稱遭到宋男性侵，甚至還跑到派出所報案。<br />\n<br />\n宋姓男子到案說明時稱，自己是被誣陷的，還直接說明自己有多花錢，且還是在女方同意之下才發生關係的，並沒有所謂的性侵。基隆地檢署檢察官認為，莉莉與被告為兩情相悅，全案不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://giant.gfycat.com/KindlyImpureAustraliancurlew.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgiant.gfycat.com%2FKindlyImpureAustraliancurlew.gif&h=949f08aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e3ca56d8ec3dfac9d54587402298bb29d50aaad","tid":392101,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"# 台灣最美的風景是人"},{"pid":"495fa149e9a60323e85d4c7ddff12960a32af1d0","tid":392101,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"點解依家風化案冇示意圖架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991c8dc0a6d44e53ba897734bcba9f4ab1a0244f","tid":392101,"uid":6314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"比哂錢都係兩情相悅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0594683af2fc76d30a1f49c8fecd3829e26c61","tid":392101,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比哂錢都係兩情相悅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明買明賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910b57a1f118db247bb18afaf4456f5089ce007e","tid":392101,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"台灣女真係俾錢就屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a554b96271b0fd50cc3fbb5647eb4de78873776e","tid":392101,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣女真係俾錢就屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80af2b37e46bbbd5fae4f5cfc937ac260ff5d41e","tid":392101,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"d奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}